title: Timestamp too early for validator registrations
body:
Some issues on devnet-10 with the validator registrations. 

mev-boost:
```
time="2023-10-24T10:36:00.295Z" level=warning msg="error calling registerValidator on relay" error="HTTP error response: 400 / {\"code\":400,\"message\":\"timestamp too early\"}\n" method=registerValidator numRegistrations=512 ua=Lodestar/v1.11.3 url="http://mev-api.dencun-devnet-10.ethpandaops.io:9062/eth/v1/builder/validators" version=v1.6.4844-dev4
```

mev-relay-api:
```
time="2023-10-24T10:36:00Z" level=warning msg="error: timestamp too early" contentLength=226305 feeRecipient=0xf97e180c050e5Ab072211Ad2C213Eb5AEE4DF134 gasLimit=30000000 headSlot=7679 method=registerValidator mevBoostV=v1.6.4844-dev4 numRegistrationsProcessed=1 numRegistrationsSoFar=1 pubkey=0x8002a0e6db224561f4aa5add29a4e5c25ab7d0de14da19959e195248c33ffc74022e84969ff599a49431f86baeaf2c56 service=relay/api signature=0x9245f9b568e9aaf6e44331e8706fb956384af44815ff8548a58cff4eac37a035e44c903a80c6a024ae9827b68d04137a124d2ef4d8aa4a01d1b91a1f1d11810ea527f55af6b03e191d7ac2fe4504eb235b2c37b13ba8334c542c7561bda689f8 timestamp="2023-10-23 08:53:36 +0000 UTC" ua="mev-boost/v1.6.4844-dev4 Lodestar/v1.11.3" version=v0.28.0-alpha2
```
